target: style_guide
validations:
  - name: palette_consistency
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that every hex color value used in the renderer, UI, and HUD drawing code
        matches a value defined in the style guide palette. No hard-coded hex values should
        appear in rendering code that are not present in the palette. Check at least:
        grass fill, path fill, water fill, HUD background, sidebar background, button colors,
        and health/happiness status bar colors. Each must trace back to a palette constant.

  - name: font_sizes_minimum
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that no text rendered on the canvas uses a font size smaller than 12px.
        The minimum readable size is 12px for tooltip body text. HUD text must be 16px.
        Menu title text must be at least 32px. Check every ctx.font assignment in the
        codebase and confirm it meets the minimum for its category as specified in the
        style guide FONTS object.

  - name: tile_size_constant
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that all tile-to-pixel and pixel-to-tile conversions use the TILE_SIZE
        constant (32) from constants.js, never a hard-coded literal 32. Search for
        multiplications and divisions by 32 in map.js, renderer.js, input.js, and
        visitors.js. Every instance should reference TILE_SIZE instead.

  - name: animation_timing
    type: agent_validation
    severity: warning
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that animal idle animation uses a 2-frame cycle at 500ms per frame (1s total)
        and visitor walk animation uses a 4-frame cycle at 200ms per frame (800ms total).
        Check the frame calculation logic in the renderer. The formulas should be:
        animalFrame = floor((tick % 1000) / 500) yielding 0 or 1, and
        visitorFrame = floor((tick % 800) / 200) yielding 0, 1, 2, or 3.

  - name: layer_ordering
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that the renderer draws layers in the correct back-to-front order:
        1) ground tiles, 2) enclosure fills, 3) enclosure borders, 4) path tiles,
        5) animals (y-sorted), 6) visitors (y-sorted), 7) build ghost overlay,
        8) UI overlays (HUD, sidebar, info bar, tooltips, toasts), 9) mini-map.
        Each layer's draw calls must complete before the next layer begins. No
        interleaving of entity types across layers.
